node.description: Prosecutors and defense lawyers for the three men accused of murdering Ahmaud Arbery made their final pitches to the jury before deliberations begin. Here is a look at their key arguments.
node.content: ["The two sides in the trial of the three men accused of murdering Ahmaud Arbery made their closing statements on Monday. Prosecutors will hold off making their rebuttal to the defense arguments until Tuesday morning, after the jury told the judge that they wanted to go home for the night. The judge also said the jury would be relocated to interior rooms in the courthouse so they would not hear the chants of demonstrators outside the courthouse.", "Here is a look at the key closing arguments."]
